getPrimeFactors

public static final long[] getPrimeFactors(long N)
Computes the prime factorization of N using brute force. Remarks ------- - Tests i <= N / i instead of i <= N for efficiency. - Tests i <= N / i instead of i * i <= N to stave off overflow and enable us to factor 9201111169755555649; otherwise program goes into infinite loop. However, i * i <= N is almost twice as fast on some systems.
